  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "F&B SERVICE CREW",
  "description": "<p><strong>Your main duties are as follows:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Welcome customers as they come into the restaurant</li>\n  <li>Provide answers to queries presented by clients regarding services and offers made available by the restaurant.</li>\n  <li>Clean all tables after clients have left and get such tables prepared for the next set of clients.</li>\n  <li>Prepare beverage and dessert and cutting of fruit for daily operation</li>\n  <li>Take beverage orders from serving staff or directly from patrons accurately &amp; promptly</li>\n  <li>Assist the restocking and replenishment of bar inventory and supplies</li>\n  <li>Maintain basic knowledge of food dishes and the pairing of sauces and sides.</li>\n  <li>Maintain responsibility for inspecting and drying of cutlery, crockery, coppers and silvers.</li>\n  <li>Ensure trays are carried and food delivered to waiter/waitresses in a timely and efficient manner.</li>\n  <li>To deliver great and excellence customer service.</li>\n  <li>Maintain quality, service &amp; cleanliness at all times according to restaurant' standards.</li>\n  <li>Adhere to hygiene and safety standards</li>\n  <li>Adhere to company’s standard operating procedures</li>\n  <li>Any other appropriate duties and responsibilities as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 6 days work week, including weekend &amp; PH.</p>",
